	<title>Questions</title>
	
	<style>
		body {
			background-image: url('../images/bground.png');
			background-repeat: no-repeat;
			background-position: center;
			background-attachment: fixed;
			background-size: cover;
			color: white;
		}
	</style>
	
</head>

<body>

	<!-- header -->
	<header>
	
	<img src="../icons/smoothie.png" alt="smoothie logo" style="vertical-align:middle; display:inline;" width="90">
		
		<div class="title">
			Smoothie Maker
		</div>
	
	<br>
		
	<a href="../index.htm" class="button" role="button">Home</a>
	<a href="get.started.htm" class="button" role="button">Products</a>
	<a href="about.us.htm" class="button" role="button">About Us</a>
	<a href="#" class="button-active" role="button" style="color: white; pointer-events: none;">Questions</a>
	
	</header>

	<br>
	
	<!-- Content Here -->
	
	<div class="container" role="main">
	
		<h1>Have a Question?</h1>
		
		<p>The form below is to fill out if you have a question or suggestion. Remember to check the <a href="about.us.htm" class="link">about us</a> page to see if the question is answered there!</p>
		
		<br>
		
		<form action="question.submit.htm">
			
			<div class="form">

				<p class="row">
					<label for="fname"> First Name: </label>
					<input type="text" id="fname" placeholder="Enter First Name" name="fname" maxlength="40">
				</p>
				
				<br>
				
				<p class="row">
					<label for="lname"> Last Name: </label>
					<input type="text" id="lname" placeholder="Enter Last Name" name="lname" maxlength="40">
				</p>
				
				<br>
					
				<p class="row">
					<label for="email"> Email: </label>
					<input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Enter Email Here" name="email" maxlength="50">
				</p>
				
				<br>
				
				<p class="row">		
					<label for="phone"> Phone Number: </label>
					<input type="tel" id="phone" placeholder="Enter Phone Number" name="phone" maxlength="10">
				</p>
				
			</div>
				
			<br>
			
			<p>Let us know your suggestion and/or question below! Please keep your language respectful and try to use proper spelling and grammar. Please be descriptive and if needed, feel free to add references.</p>
			
			<br>
			
			<div class="form">
				
				<p class="row">
					<input type="radio" id="question" name="question" value="question">
					<label for="question"> Question </label>
					
					<input type="radio" id="suggestion" name="question" value="suggestion">
					<label for="suggestion"> Suggestion </label>
					
					<input type="radio" id="both" name="question" value="both">
					<label for="both"> Both </label>
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<br>
			<br>
				
			<textarea id="information" placeholder="Don't be shy" name="information" cols="90" rows="10" maxlength="1000" style="text-align: left; font-size: 20px; font-family: 'Shadows Into Light Two', cursive; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; border-radius: 10px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px; border-radius: 10px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;
			
			@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {border: 2px solid black;  color: white; background-color: grey;} 
			
			@media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {border: 2px solid white; color: black;"></textarea>
			
		</form>
		
		<a href="question.submit.htm" class="orange-button" role="button">SUBMIT</a>
		
	</div>
	
	<br>
	<br>
	<br>
	<br>
	
